**You are sitting on a beautiful white sandy beach with crystal-clear light blue-ish green water gently lapping at your toes. The warm sun beats down on your skin, and a gentle breeze carries the salty sea air past you. As you sit, you look up and see the most breathtaking view of the green and blue milky way in the night sky, twinkling and shining brightly against the dark backdrop. The stars seem to go on forever, creating a sense of awe and wonder within you. The art style of this scene is vibrant and dreamy, with bright colors and a soft, almost ethereal quality. The sky is a swirl of bright greens and blues, and the stars sparkle like diamonds. The sand is a pure white, and the water is so clear you can see the tiny fish swimming around your feet. The palm trees that line the beach are full and lush, their leaves rustling in the gentle breeze. The overall effect is one of magic and wonder, a dream-like world that seems almost too beautiful to be real. You take a deep breath and let yourself fully relax into the serene and peaceful surroundings, feeling grateful for this moment of pure natural beauty. You feel as if you are in a beautiful painting, a masterpiece of color and light that will stay with you forever.** - <@531326782482284545> (fast)
